= Locations =

This page documents all locations in Dragon Warrior for the NES.

== Overview ==

Dragon Warrior takes place in the kingdom of Alefgard, a land threatened by the Dragonlord. The hero must explore the overworld, towns, and dungeons to rescue Princess Gwaelin and defeat the Dragonlord.

